The tf.SparseTensor API has changed between the 0.12 release and the git master. You should run the version of wide_n_deep_tutorial.py from the r0.12 branch when you have TensorFlow 0.12 installed:

https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/r0.12/tensorflow/examples/learn/wide_n_deep_tutorial.py

The `tf.SparseTensor` API has changed between the 0.12 release and the git master. You should run the version of `wide_n_deep_tutorial.py` from the `r0.12` branch when you have TensorFlow 0.12 installed:

https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/r0.12/tensorflow/examples/learn/wide_n_deep_tutorial.py
